{"tid":1464344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［813機場］發現左兄弟爬山既弱點","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:10:10.000Z","uid":87790,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd04959ea02047f14a8447b4c2b501812269a904","tid":1464344,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山既弱點似乎係玩鬼，尊重大家做法既背後就係點都要攬，到最後比人帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰 不分化 係對同路人既態度。<br />\n<br />\n但打記者，甚至連醫護都打個d係咪同路人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去到今時今日兩個月，除左警察同黑社會有無一個黑衫打過記者同醫護？</span><br />\n<br />\n到底不割蓆不篤灰不分化既前提是咪應該判別佢係咪同路人？ 定要無限量信任？<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，我亦絕對明白一玩捉鬼就會分化。但如果對家出呢招，大家要點樣應對呢？<br />\n<br />\n真心講，我寫呢段野既同時都好想知答案，唔識評論，只能請教。"},{"pid":"3cd817f392159d61cadb44a6226f150511117e96","tid":1464344,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"154858c6033f3902a4b2ae33422daa73df1e3942","tid":1464344,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YHUDBoMHBQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYHUDBoMHBQk&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2jUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=68c4d89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YHUDBoMHBQk</a><br />\n呢條片都有講啦"},{"pid":"1e4437c7296269e6bd31645cb01639a64beace03","tid":1464344,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcebd7d0e68b03d36398de55822192b31ff50e36","tid":1464344,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"154858c6033f3902a4b2ae33422daa73df1e3942","tid":1464344,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YHUDBoMHBQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYHUDBoMHBQk&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2jUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=6